"full_signature": "public BuiltInValueTree BUILT_IN_VALUE()", "class_method_signature": "JsonGrammar.BUILT_IN_VALUE()", "testcase": false, "constructor": false}], "file": "sslr-examples/src/main/java/org/sonar/sslr/examples/grammars/typed/JsonGrammar.java"}, "focal_method": {"identifier": "OBJECT", "parameters": "()", "modifiers": "public", "return": "ObjectTree", "body": "public ObjectTree OBJECT() {\n    return b.<ObjectTree>nonterminal(JsonLexer.OBJECT).is(\n      f.object(\n        b.token(JsonLexer.LCURLYBRACE),\n        b.optional(PAIR_LIST()),\n        b.token(JsonLexer.RCURLYBRACE)));\n  }", "signature": "ObjectTree OBJECT()", "full_signature": "public ObjectTree OBJECT()", "class_method_signature": "JsonGrammar.OBJECT()", "testcase": false, "constructor": false, "invocations": ["is", "nonterminal", "object", "token", "optional", "PAIR_LIST", "token"]}, "repository": {"repo_id": 4159017, "url": "https://github.com/SonarSource/sslr", "language": "Java", "is_fork": false, "fork_count": 28, "stargazer_count": 51, "size": 5875, "license": "licensed"}}